      <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <h2 class="roboto-bold" style="color: white;">Marketplace for Gallery Spaces:</h2>
      <p class="roboto-regular" style="color: white;"><strong>Kollab</strong> allows users to explore a diverse marketplace of gallery spaces available for rent across Tokyo. Artists can browse various options, comparing spaces based on size, location, price, and amenities, making it easy to find the perfect venue for their exhibitions.</p>
      <h2 class="roboto-bold" style="color: white;">Real-Time Communication:</h2>

      <p class="roboto-regular" style="color: white;">To improve user interaction, Kollab incorporates a real-time communication system. Artists and gallery owners can easily communicate to ask questions, confirm details, or discuss booking arrangements directly through the app. This feature ensures a smooth transaction and booking process for both parties.</p>

      <h2 class="roboto-bold" style="color: white;">Gallery Registration and Management:</h2>

      <p class="roboto-regular" style="color: white;">Gallery owners can register their spaces, list them for rent, and manage bookings all within the platform. With integrated tools for adding images, descriptions, pricing, and availability, managing your gallery’s listings becomes effortless.</p>

      <h2 class="roboto-bold" style="color: white;">Booking and Event Organization:</h2>

      <p class="roboto-regular" style="color: white;">Artists can easily book a gallery space for their upcoming exhibitions. With Kollab, all the logistics of securing a venue are handled within the app. Artists can schedule the rental period, receive confirmation, and keep track of their bookings to ensure everything is ready for their showcase.</p>

      <h2 class="roboto-bold" style="color: white;">Collaborative Ecosystem:</h2>

      <p class="roboto-regular" style="color: white;">Kollab’s focus on collaboration makes it an ideal platform for artists looking to display their work in a shared, creative environment. By integrating various services into the app, such as communication and payment, Kollab fosters an ecosystem where gallery owners and artists can seamlessly collaborate.</p>


      <p class="roboto-regular" style="color: white;">This app is perfect for anyone in Tokyo’s vibrant art scene looking to rent or list gallery spaces, providing a convenient and centralized platform to meet the needs of both artists and gallery owners alike.</p>
